# Project Overview

## Product Description
We are building a journaling and mood tracking web application with AI-generated reflections. This app helps users track their mental health through daily journaling and mood logging, with AI-powered insights available for premium users.

## Core Features
- **Journal entries**: Create, edit, and delete personal journal entries
- **Mood logging**: Track daily moods and emotional states
- **Timeline view**: Unified view of journal entries and mood history
- **AI insights**: AI-generated reflections and insights (paid feature)
- **Search functionality**: Search through entries and tags

## User Limits
- **Free tier**: 5 journal entries per day, 3 mood logs per day
- **AI features**: Premium/paid feature only

## Target Users
Individuals interested in mental health tracking, self-reflection, and personal growth through journaling and mood awareness.

## Key Pages
- Landing page (`/`)
- Dashboard overview (`/dashboard`)
- Journal entries management (`/journal`)
- Mood tracking interface (`/mood`)
- Analytics and insights (`/analytics`)
- User settings (`/settings`)